<div class="hero-unit">
	<h1>enter the cloud. enter codebender.</h1>
	<p>Time to revolutionize the way you develop and hack on your projects. {{site_name}} is a platform that helps your next idea come to life. Wether you are a maker, a hardware hacker or an artist, {{ site_name }} allows you to code on the web, faster and easier, using our awesome web editor. Host your Arduino sketches on the cloud and use our next-gen compiler to build and debug your sketches from your browser. When you are done, upload them to your Arduino, straight from your browser. No installations required. <!--Give it a try, join the cloud today. --><strong>Coming soon. Stay tuned!</strong></p>
